<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">THE LEA=
P YEAR CALCULATOR&nbsp;</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">Is it a=
 leap year? What about in 1900? Or 2100?<br class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text"=
>
Get your Leap Year facts straight with this Leap Year calculator.<br class=
=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
Just enter the year you are interested in and the script reports whether it=
 is&nbsp;a Leap Year or not.</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">&nbsp;<=
/p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">Or, ent=
er a range of years and JavaScript will display all the Leap Years in that =
range. It's Leaparific!</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;"><span c=
lass=3D"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">=E2=80=8B</span></p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">Check F=
or Leap Year:<br class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
Year:&nbsp;&nbsp;is&nbsp;<br class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
Enter the year then click the button below.</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;"><br cla=
ss=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
Leap Years Within A Range:</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">Start Y=
ear:&nbsp;<br class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
End Year:&nbsp;</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">&nbsp;<=
/p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;">There's=
 7 days a week, a Leap Year every 4 years, so every 28 years,<br class=3D"w=
ixui-rich-text__text">
Leap Day falls on the same day, and that day occurs 5 times that month.<br =
class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
It happens every 28 years. This is a cycle that began in 1904 and ends in 2=
096.</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;"><br cla=
ss=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
This pattern works so long as there is a Leap&nbsp;Year every 4 years...<br=
 class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">
In 2100, the pattern will be broken, and a new 28 year cycle starts in 2104=
.</p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:18px;"><br cla=
